data.description: Discover modern comfort in this single family, ranch-style home, thoughtfully updated and designed for comfortable living. With a downstairs bar and finished basement living space, this residence is an entertainer's delight. The main floor host a nice living room, dining space, kitchen, 3 bedrooms and a full bath. The basement has a large entertaining or relaxing space in a living room and wet bar. You will also love the fully redone bathroom. Don't forget about the convenience of the two-car garage, back deck, and large yard space on a great corner lot with mature trees and shrubbery. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours – schedule a showing today!
